<bibRefCitation id="250352219534A171E19234F4CBAD1144" DOI="https://doi.org/10.25223/brad.n28.2010.a6" author="Klopper, RR" journalOrPublisher="Bradleya" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="37 - 38" refId="B25" refString="Klopper, RR, Zietsman, PC, Du Preez, PJ, Smith, GF, 2010. A first record of a South African aloe, Aloe spectabilis, becoming naturalised elsewhere in the country. Bradleya 28: 37 - 38, DOI: https://doi.org/10.25223/brad.n28.2010.a6" title="A first record of a South African aloe, Aloe spectabilis, becoming naturalised elsewhere in the country." url="https://doi.org/10.25223/brad.n28.2010.a6" volume="28" year="2010">Klopper et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
